snippet: LEAD: The state official leading the fight to carry out California's first execution in 23 years said Saturday that the Supreme Court had agreed to consider an appeal of a ruling that blocked the death sentence....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: The state official leading the fight to carry out California's first execution in 23 years said Saturday that the Supreme Court had agreed to consider an appeal of a ruling that blocked the death sentence.

headline.main: Supreme Court Said to Agree To Take California Death Case
